attributes.review: I understand that this is Trump’s app but the news published on it is more opinion based than fact based. Everything portrays Trump in the best possible way, skewing the truth. If you want to actually stay up to date on the news I suggest using the Apple News app instead!

attributes.title: Not even Free is it worth it
attributes.review: Absolutely terrible design. It keeps trying to get my number and I honestly don’t need any more scam calls. The background is just an eyesore. I don’t know who was in charge of design, but they need to get replaced ASAP! As for the download itself, Jesus! It kept saying it was finished and then it would just keep restarting. It was a never ending cycle that I could’ve lived without. I had to get bribed to even open the app after that experience. Then it was even worse after opening it lol all I did was just laugh after that. But serious, not worth your time. STAY AWAY!
